id: "class:rogue#driver"
name: "Driver"
description: "A driver makes her living driving vehicles in the service of those who\
  \ can pay for her considerable talents. She may be a wagon-driver practiced at smuggling\
  \ contraband, an accomplished musher blazing arctic trails, or a seemingly refined\
  \ coach driver placing her roguish talents in the service of a wealthy patron."
modifications:
